window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>WARNING: This Book Will Fill You With Intense and Relentless Sexual Desire. Intended for Adult Audiences Only! Listen at Your Own Risk.</p> <p>*****VOLUME TWO*****</p> <p>Chayse is a 6 foot tall, Big Beautiful Woman. She would have preferred shooting buck, riding her horses and bouncing around on her land rover than going to Harvard Business School. But due to her father’s influence, she spent 5 years working night and day to get her Master’s Degree with honours. When Chayse returns home, she bumps into someone she hasn’t seen in years.</p> <p>Bourden and Chayse had been childhood friends and neither had thought much about each other over the past 13 years. But when they became reacquainted it was like melting hot iron between them. The chemistry was intense, and neither knew how to handle it. But that was before Chayse learned Bourden’s family secret and realized that even after all these years, they both were still in love with each other, and their passion for each other was unstoppable. They could not resist the animal magnetism between the two of them. But would Bourden’s family secret end up tearing them apart?</p>"; 
